:PROFILE [image:cover.jpg]
Bessel van der Kolk
Boston, Massachusetts
Psychiatrist and trauma researcher. Founder of the Trauma Center. Author of \
The Body Keeps the Score, published in 2014.

:NOTE
This is not a book to read during a hard season without support around you. \
It will surface things. Have someone to talk to before you begin.

